Proxima, Corner of Hill Street and Stanley Lane

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Gold Coast and Transact Property are delighted to present to the market the first commercial office and medical leasing opportunity within Lumina - the Gold Coast Health and Knowledge Precinct’s commercial hub that adjoins the Gold Coast University Hospital, Griffith University and the Gold Coast University Private Hospital.

Offering seven levels of architecturally designed office and medical amenity, Proxima will provide the opportunity for commercial office users, specialised health providers, researchers, consultants and carers to work together by offering office, research, allied health, childcare and training facilities under one roof within a purpose-built building in a dedicated and world-renowned health, research and business precinct.

Current Availabilities:
Ground floor tenancies ranging from 60m² to 550m²
Commercial office and medical tenancies ranging from 100m² to 5,500m²

Expected Project Completion:
- Late 2022

Features Include:
- 200 place childcare facility within the building
- 143 underground car parks
- NABERS 5 Star Energy Commitment Agreement
- Under 100 metres to Woolworths anchored shopping centre
- Walking distance from the Gold Coast Light Rail and bus interchange
- Ground floor café

Please contact the listed agenst for a copy of the information memorandum or for a confidential discussion as to how we can assist you and your business to be a part of Proxima.
